---
---

<section class="section-pad" id="features">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="kicker">Calm tools, quietly powerful</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Everything you need to start the day <span class="accent">with intention</span></h2>
      <p class="section-desc">No overwhelming task lists. No artificial deadlines. Just the few things that help you focus — beautifully arranged on every new tab.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-grid">
      <div class="feat glass reveal">
        <div class="feat-icon" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#8B5CF6,#6d28d9)"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10 11h.01M14 11h.01M3 5v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8l-3-3H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2"/><path d="M16 3v4M8 3v4"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Daily Wisdom</h3>
        <p>A hand-picked quote on every tab, sorted into ten life categories — from creativity to resilience. Favorite the ones that land.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat glass reveal">
        <div class="feat-icon" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#10B981,#059669)"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Today's Focus</h3>
        <p>Capture what matters most in seconds and watch your progress fill as the day unfolds. Momentum you can actually see.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat glass reveal">
        <div class="feat-icon" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#F59E0B,#d97706)"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10 2h4"/><path d="M12 14v-4"/><circle cx="12" cy="14" r="8"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Pomodoro Timer</h3>
        <p>Focus for 25 minutes, then breathe for 5. A calm, full-screen timer that keeps your rhythm without the noise.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat glass reveal">
        <div class="feat-icon" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#3B82F6,#2563eb)"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 3v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16"/><path d="M18 17V9M13 17V5M8 17v-3"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Insights</h3>
        <p>Streaks, goals completed and the categories you return to most — gentle stats that celebrate progress, never shame it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat glass reveal">
        <div class="feat-icon" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#EC4899,#db2777)"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 8a6 6 0 0 1 12 0c0 7 3 9 3 9H3s3-2 3-9"/><path d="M10.3 21a1.94 1.94 0 0 0 3.4 0"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Reminders</h3>
        <p>Stay on top of what matters with gentle, repeatable nudges — overdue and upcoming, always one glance away.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat glass reveal">
        <div class="feat-icon" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#06B6D4,#0891b2)"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="13.5" cy="6.5" r=".5" fill="currentColor"/><circle cx="17.5" cy="10.5" r=".5" fill="currentColor"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="7.5" r=".5" fill="currentColor"/><circle cx="6.5" cy="12.5" r=".5" fill="currentColor"/><path d="M12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12s4.5 10 10 10c.926 0 1.648-.746 1.648-1.688 0-.437-.18-.835-.437-1.125-.29-.289-.438-.652-.438-1.125a1.64 1.64 0 0 1 1.668-1.668h1.996c3.051 0 5.563-2.512 5.563-5.563C21.999 6.012 17.5 2 12 2z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Four Themes</h3>
        <p>Purple, Forest, Rose, or this signature Glass mode — frosted cards over a fresh daily photo. Make every tab yours.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
